                <h2>Bayesian Optimization<br>Basket Trading</h2>
                <p>Go beyond simple p-values and static thresholds. This project models live trading performance as a
                    black-box function, utilizing the Optuna framework to execute Bayesian Optimization. It searches a
                    multi-dimensional parameter space to hunt for the global maxima of Sharpe ratios, controlling for
                    optimal lookback windows, dynamic entry/exit Z-scores, and capital allocations across cointegrated
                    baskets to ensure robust out-of-sample performance.</p>
