                <h2>Smart Predict-then-Optimize (SPO)</h2>
                <p>Why optimize for mere statistical prediction accuracy when the ultimate goal is financial returns?
                    The SPO framework forces a PyTorch Neural Network to directly minimize portfolio decision loss. By
                    coupling forecasting layers directly to a differentiable Softmax allocator, this approach enables
                    end-to-end training that aligns asset return forecasting natively with the actual downstream
                    Mean-Variance optimization outcome.</p>
